			<li>Brush teeth</li>
			<li>Comb hair</li>
			<li>Dusting</li>
		</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="guide-example">
			<h3>Chore Chart Ideas for Kids 7-12</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Wash and put away laundry</li>
				<li>Feed pets</li>
